descriptionHtml:
Blizzard home is a home located at "Anga`s Mill" west of Windhelm (see screenshot)

There are...

A)10 Mannequins
B)20 Weapon Racks ( 4 Sets that hold 5 each)
C)8 Large Display Cases
D)8 Shield Plaques
E)10 Weapon Plaques

A)The Crates that have veg in them are functional storage containers
B)The shelves with potions and gem souls are are also functional storage containers
D)The Table with ingots are functional storage containers
E)The barrels are functional storage containers
F)The sacks are of course are functional storage containers and any other chests, etc. are functional storage containers
E)All of the ingredient jars have been renamed for all various ingredients and are also functional storage containers

If you encounter any bugs or have any suggestions then please comment

If you like Blizzard Shack then please comment and endor.
